        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "For these users, tutorials and automated overviews can be developed. The user invokes a software program or procedure that explains the major system functions step by step. Sometimes a document is combined with a special program; the user reads about the function first and then exercises the next step in the program to perform the function.",
                "img_id": null
