        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "For example, users who know how to use a keyboard can skip typing modules, and operators familiar with computer concepts need not study what each peripheral does. Review modules can be developed for those already familiar with some functions.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Users who know how to use a keyboard can skip the modules on typing, and operators who are well-versed in computer concepts need not study the module on what each peripheral does. Review modules can be developed for those who are already familiar with some functions.",
