            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Ying, an intuitive introvert, also thrives on her colleagues' attention. She is sensitive and aware of her emotional reactions to people and problems; it is very important that she be liked by her peers. Because she is a good listener, Ying is the project member to whom others turn to express their feelings. Ying takes a lot of time to make a decision, not only because she needs complete information, but also because she wants to make the right decision.",
                "img_id": null
